metadata.name: Top G Pizza
metadata.description:
3,333 Top G Pizza's immortalizing the day the Top G was taken down.

Did they finally get him, or will the Top G rise again?

P.s - You get absolutely f*cking NOTHING for owning this NFT. You are a lucky little punk to have the chance to grace your wallet with a slice of this Top G Pizza.

attributes.value: Water. Wot, did you think you were gettin' a fu*ckin' soda?
Garden Salad. Top G's take care of their bodies. It is your temple after all.
